you are given a source code to test and it randomly crashes and it never crashes in the same place . explain what all you would suspect and how would you go about with isolating the cause.

Sol-

  given a source code to test is randomly crashes because of the following reasons - 
- Not initialising a variable but attempting to use its value. 
- Dereferencing a null pointer. 
- Reading or writing past the end of an array.
